CAMPARI offers a 2 stateroom, 2 head layout. Additional upgrades to the vessel include:
• Seakeeper 6
• 2021 Stainless Lewmar 35# Plow Anchor + 200' G4 Chain
• Full Service Volvo D6 (351hrs) + Fischer Panda 12KW Generator (483hrs)
